{"tid":2288865,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"喜茶分店被破壞 16 歲男願意用買千元零用錢賠償","createTime":"2020-11-16T23:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T01:11:10.000Z","uid":230530,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e719df0803a3de667069d4ade293a44704d473","tid":2288865,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T23:30:03.000Z","msg":"網民早前號召到各區商場「和你Sing」並「賀」行政長官林鄭月娥生辰。其中在沙田新城市廣場，內地品牌連鎖茶店「喜茶」舖內設施遭人破壞，一名16歲少年當場被捕。他今在沙田裁判法院承認一項刑事毀壞罪，並願意以自己省下的零用錢向喜茶賠償。署理主任裁判官溫紹明將案件押後至下月7日判刑，其間准許被告保釋，等候感化官及社會服務令報告。<br />\n<br />\n認罪被告姓周（16歲），原本被控一項刑事毀壞及一項抗拒正在正當執行職務的警務人員罪，他今承認首罪，控方同意就另一罪撤控。<br />\n<br />\n間野都執左賠條撚？😂"},{"pid":"e75629582b3d5faca299130b76402b9d42a6e99c","tid":2288865,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T23:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59b245827c4effa0d09ba4fae67a09ac57d3e99","tid":2288865,"uid":225422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T23:32:29.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"e44afe17623fa12e6dc8b28eba5a190f9d1c7b26","tid":2288865,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T23:36:08.000Z","msg":"認左刑事毀壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁後生應該又係判勞教"},{"pid":"d5ee958618987b1ccc5ad5ac3b5d6e6f2f560199","tid":2288865,"uid":24909,"like":4,"dislike":28,"score":-24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T23:45:37.000Z","msg":"間野都冇人飲架啦 同埋都早知實有99伏係度 果然係16歳 on99咁"},{"pid":"d2ecaec05dca886a7ce168527cd8d12eb859ac29","tid":2288865,"uid":294632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T23:48:02.000Z","msg":"庭外和解 果日營業額都冇一千"},{"pid":"30b7d4a589e035c0efa88269892f52f32c1d4f40","tid":2288865,"uid":84102,"l